milestones.description: Angus Fraser and Phil Tufnell's 43-run partnership is ENG's highest for the 10th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 30 between John Lever and Bairstow
Allan Border has broken the record for most catches (99) in ODIs, going past Viv Richards's 98
